OL,6,FOn Tuesday 30 January, police executed
OL,7,Ffour warrants and have arrested a man
OL,8,Fand a woman.
OL,10,FOfficers recovered a large amount of
OL,11,Fcash, suspected Class A drugs and
OL,12,Fmultiple mobile phones at an address
OL,13,Fin Old Swan and items associated with
OL,14,Fthe supply of drugs.
OL,16,FA 53-year-old man from Garston was
OL,17,Farrested on suspicion of possession
OL,18,Fwith intent to supply crack cocaine
OL,19,Fand heroin, and possession of criminal
OL,20,Fproperty. He is now being questioned
OL,21,Fby police.
