OL,4,Cshot in the face inside a flat
OL,6,FA woman, 51, has been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of possession of a
OL,8,Fcontrolled drug.JDetective Chief
OL,9,FInspector John Fitzgerald said: "The
OL,10,Finvestigation into this shooting is
OL,11,Fstill in the early stages but we
OL,12,Fbelieve it was a targeted attack.
OL,14,F"We are continuing to carry out CCTV
OL,15,Fand house-to-house enquiries to
OL,16,Festablish exactly what happened.
