OL,4,Cshot in the face inside a flat
OL,6,F"We understand the fear that gun crime
OL,7,Fcauses and I'd like to assure
OL,8,Fresidents living in the area that the
OL,9,Fuse of firearms will not be tolerated
OL,10,Fon the streets of Merseyside.
OL,12,F"We are committed to tackling gun
OL,13,Fcrime and will pursue those who are
OL,14,Fprepared to use firearms to endanger
OL,15,Fthe lives of people in our community.
OL,16,F"In the 12 months to September 2023,
OL,17,Fwe saw a 50% reduction in firearms
OL,18,Foffences compared the previous year.
